Titulo: La0.6PrSr0.4NiO4-Ce0.8Pr0.2O2 composite cathode for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: (x = 0, 10, 20, 30, 40, 50), abbreviated as LPSN-xCPO, were prepared and used as composite cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell (IT-SOFC).
Titulo: La0.6PrSr0.4NiO4-Ce0.8Pr0.2O2 composite cathode for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: XRD result suggested that no chemical reaction occurred between LPSN and CPO after sintering at 1200 degrees C for 4 h. Electrical conductivity of LPSN-xCPO decreased with x. LPSN-40CPO exhibited the best performance on cathode impedance spectra under open-circuit condition.
Titulo: La0.6PrSr0.4NiO4-Ce0.8Pr0.2O2 composite cathode for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: At 700 degrees C, Exchange current density of LPSN-40CPO and LPSN was 50.1 and 15.8 mA
Titulo: La0.6PrSr0.4NiO4-Ce0.8Pr0.2O2 composite cathode for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: cm(-2), respectively, and the polarization resistance R-P of LPSN-40CPO was 0.22 Omega cm(2), which is about one-eighth of that of LPSN.
Titulo: La0.6PrSr0.4NiO4-Ce0.8Pr0.2O2 composite cathode for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The OCV of the cell with LPSN-40CPO as cathode was about 0.78 V, and the maximum of power density was about 88 mW cm(-2).
Titulo: La0.6PrSr0.4NiO4-Ce0.8Pr0.2O2 composite cathode for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: LPSN-40CPO can be a promise candidate for cathode in IT-SOFC.
Titulo: La0.6PrSr0.4NiO4-Ce0.8Pr0.2O2 composite cathode for solid oxide fuel cell
